                            <div id="dnn_ContentPane"><div class="DnnModule DnnModule-DNN_HTML DnnModule-2521"><a name="2521"></a><div id="dnn_ctr2521_ContentPane"><!-- Start_Module_2521 --><div id="dnn_ctr2521_ModuleContent" class="DNNModuleContent ModDNNHTMLC">
	<div id="dnn_ctr2521_HtmlModule_lblContent" class="Normal">
	<h2>Surplus Automotive Public Auctions</h2>
All vehicles may be inspected on the morning of the auction from 7:30 a.m. until 9:00 a.m. Auctions start promptly at 9:00 a.m. The next Surplus Automotive Auction date&nbsp;is&nbsp;tentatively scheduled for <strong>Wednesday, October 9, 2013.</strong><br />
<br />
<a href="http://www.arb.ca.gov/msprog/publicfleets/retirement.htm ">Fleet Rule for Public Agencies and Utilities - Vehicle Retirement<br />
</a><br />
To receive notification of upcoming auctions, subscribe your e-mail address to the DGS Office of Fleet and Asset Management (OFAM) Surplus Automotive Equipment Auction page: <br />
<br />
<strong><span style="color: #ff0000;">*&nbsp;<a href="/ofam/Programs/StSurplus/Auctions/AutoAuction/Subscribe.aspx" title="Subscribe to receive notification of upcoming auction information"><span style="color: #ff0000;">Subscribe to the Surplus Automotive Public Auction</span></a></span><span style="color: #ff0000;"> *</span></strong> <br />
<br />
</div>

</div><!-- End_Module_2521 --></div>
